metadata.description:
HANAFUDA'S TIME - Cherry Blossom

Inspired by the Japanese card game Hanafuda, Cherry Blossom represents one of the card's type of the game: Cherry blossoms.

Cherry Blossom will change every phase of the day:  
1st phase: 0 - 5am  
2nd phase: 6 - 11am  
3rd stage: 1 - 5pm  
4th stage: 6pm - 11pm
